---
title: Creamy Potato-Topped Lamb Hotpot with Melted Cheese & Sour Cream
description: Creamy, indulgent and bursting with wholesome flavours, our creamy potato topped lamb hotpot is exactly what you need on a cold night.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-potato-topped-lamb-hotpot-d8f5e1b0-26a9c632.jpg
